    <h1>Review Diversity</h1>
    <p class="description">Distributing customer reviews across multiple platforms — Google, Yelp, Facebook, industry-specific sites — rather than concentrating them on a single source. Reduces platform risk and <strong>reinforces local SEO signals</strong> from multiple directions.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
